{"_id":"f4c1a20cf6af8dfc","name":"Effect: Dog Pile","type":"effect","img":"icons/svg/aura.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks to Grapple, Shove, or Trip while flanking the bounty hunter's hunted prey.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Archetypes: Wilderness"},"rules":[{"key":"FlatModifier","selector":"athletics","type":"circumstance","value":2,"label":"Dog Pile","predicate":[{"or":["action:grapple","action:shove","action:trip"]}]}],"slug":"effect-dog-pile","schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2026-04-08T15:18:47.755Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"level":{"value":10},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"6.0.0","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1775661527743,"modifiedTime":1775661527743,"lastModifiedBy":"generator"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"465a1877f36546c4","name":"Effect: Darken Tone","type":"effect","img":"icons/svg/aura.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You gain a status bonus to damage rolls equal to the number of your weapon's damage dice. When you critically hit an enemy, the enemy becomes frightened 1.</p><p><em>Note: The damage bonus defaults to 1. Adjust if your weapon has more damage dice.</em></p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Archetypes: Wilderness"},"rules":[{"key":"FlatModifier","selector":"strike-damage","type":"status","value":1,"label":"Darken Tone (adjust to weapon dice count)"},{"key":"Note","selector":"strike-attack-roll","text":"<p class=\"compact-text\"><strong>Darken Tone</strong> On a critical hit, the enemy becomes frightened 1.</p>","outcome":["criticalSuccess"]}],"slug":"effect-darken-tone","schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2026-04-08T15:18:47.755Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"level":{"value":8},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"6.0.0","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1775661527743,"modifiedTime":1775661527743,"lastModifiedBy":"generator"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"7b1a8673d2df148c","name":"Effect: Lighten Tone","type":"effect","img":"icons/svg/heal.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You gain temporary HP equal to half the folklorist's level. Once per round when you damage the villain, regain these temporary HP.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Archetypes: Wilderness"},"rules":[{"key":"TempHP","value":"floor(@actor.level/2)"},{"key":"Note","selector":"strike-damage","text":"<p class=\"compact-text\"><strong>Lighten Tone</strong> Once per round when you damage the Spin Tale villain, regain TempHP equal to half the folklorist's level.</p>"}],"slug":"effect-lighten-tone","schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2026-04-08T15:18:47.756Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"level":{"value":8},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"6.0.0","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1775661527743,"modifiedTime":1775661527743,"lastModifiedBy":"generator"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"e92b9bdf0db0e7e9","name":"Effect: Establish Foil","type":"effect","img":"icons/svg/eye.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>This creature is a foil of the Spin Tale. The hero gains their Spin Tale status bonus to attacks and damage against this creature in addition to the original villain.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Archetypes: Wilderness"},"rules":[],"slug":"effect-establish-foil","schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2026-04-08T15:18:47.756Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"level":{"value":6},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"6.0.0","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1775661527743,"modifiedTime":1775661527743,"lastModifiedBy":"generator"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"fa93b46a79999283","name":"Effect: Establish Foil (Ally)","type":"effect","img":"icons/svg/aura.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You are an ally foil of the Spin Tale. The hero gains a +1 status bonus to checks to Aid you. Each time you take damage, reduce it by 5 (10 at master Performance, 15 at legendary) — the Spin Tale hero takes that damage instead (unreducible).</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Archetypes: Wilderness"},"rules":[{"key":"Note","selector":"ac","text":"<p class=\"compact-text\"><strong>Establish Foil</strong> When you take damage, reduce by 5/10/15. The Spin Tale hero takes that unreducible damage instead.</p>"}],"slug":"effect-establish-foil-ally","schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2026-04-08T15:18:47.756Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"level":{"value":6},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"6.0.0","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1775661527743,"modifiedTime":1775661527743,"lastModifiedBy":"generator"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"b7e64737c5fa8b5b","name":"Effect: Cast of Villains Foil","type":"effect","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You take a -2 status penalty to attack rolls and skill checks against targets that are not the hero of the Spin Tale.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Archetypes: Wilderness"},"rules":[{"key":"FlatModifier","selector":"attack-roll","type":"status","value":-2,"label":"Cast of Villains Foil"},{"key":"FlatModifier","selector":"skill-check","type":"status","value":-2,"label":"Cast of Villains Foil"},{"key":"Note","selector":"attack-roll","text":"<p class=\"compact-text\"><strong>Cast of Villains</strong> This penalty does NOT apply against the Spin Tale hero.</p>"}],"slug":"effect-cast-of-villains-foil","schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2026-04-08T15:18:47.756Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"level":{"value":12},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"6.0.0","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1775661527743,"modifiedTime":1775661527743,"lastModifiedBy":"generator"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"eb0211e6e2a91446","name":"Effect: Second Act (Off-Guard)","type":"effect","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>This creature is off-guard to the hero of the Spin Tale for 1 round.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Archetypes: Wilderness"},"rules":[],"slug":"effect-second-act-off-guard","schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2026-04-08T15:18:47.756Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"level":{"value":10},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"duration":{"value":1,"unit":"rounds","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"6.0.0","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1775661527743,"modifiedTime":1775661527743,"lastModifiedBy":"generator"},"schemaVersion":13}
